<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als mir
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat
              von der sache wegen, als <add><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade mit mir und</add> ich
              mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <add>zu <expan>Mergenth<ex>eim</ex></expan>
                miteinander</add> geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und wie ewr edell
                  <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> in die Vaytland reyten müsze, und
                  <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> darausz kumt, daz ir
                  <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> her czu mir zu reyten maint, das han ich wol
                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan></del>Edler
            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ewr gnade und ich <expan>miteinand<ex>er</ex></expan>
            czu Mergentheim geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade, als ir mir <expan>ges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> habt,
                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> in die Vaytland reyten müsz und
                <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wider darausz kumt, daz
            ir <add>mich</add>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das wissen lassen und czu mir her <add>zu</add> reyten
              <add>maint</add>, das alles han ich wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
            lasz <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade wissen, daz des gar czu vil wer, daz
                  <add><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell</add> czu mir her reyten solt,
                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> ir ausz der vaytland kumt, so mügt ir wol
                <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> getrawet, her zu mir
                <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan>, der <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> von den <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mir erczel. So
            wil ich das <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> an <add>etlich</add> mein freunde bringen
              <add>und mit im <expan>fürb<ex>as</ex></expan> darausz reden</add> und wo ich
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> in den oder <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.
                <lb/><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>a</ex>ll<ex>e</ex>r</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
